My teak outdoor table was looking real dry and thirsty. So I gave it a refresh with three easy steps.

1. Power wash with water and wood sage tip.
2. Sand with 120 followed by 220.
3. Wipe on @rustoleum Watco Teak Oil + Stain

Took me about 5 hours and was totally worth it!

From Vanity to Nightstands! ✨ Say goodbye to boring old vanities and hello to stylish nightstands! 

I took this vintage vanity and cut it in half to create two stunning nightstands that will add a touch of charm to my daughter’s bedroom. But the real game-changer was using my Wagner FLEXiO 3500 paint sprayer! 

Spraying is a whopping 10x faster than painting by hand, and the finish is incredibly smooth and flawless. 🤩✨ Plus, it’s a total time-saver, which was a blessing after all that prep work.

#furnitureflip #nightstands #burgundy #furnituremakeover

We are going on week 3 of this system, and it’s still clean! That is a record for my family.

We spent the week between Christmas and New Year’s aboard one of the biggest ships at sea, @royalcaribbean Allure of the Seas. 

We have been into providing experiences over stuff in the past couple of years, and we made some incredible memories on this vacation.

All three kids tried snorkeling in deep water, we did a scavenger hunt in St. Maarten and came in dead last 😜, two of the kids tried snails (escargot) on French night and learned how to order off the adult menu at dinner. 

My favorites included the silent family disco, trivia, family karaoke, the water show Oceanaria, and the production of Mama Mia. I’ve got all those Abba songs stuck in my head ever since.

My dislikes were…It was hard to get the kids leave the room sometimes. I think there is so much to do you sometimes get overwhelmed or feel like you can’t relax. It’s a real hassle trying to get chairs on deck by the pool in the sun. And I was pretty queazy the first two days getting my sea legs. 

Cruising is definitely a culture…do you cruise? Tell me what you love about and what ships you like!

#notsponsored #travelfamilyof5 #whatiearned #firsttimecruiser #royalcaribbean #allureoftheseas #cruisevacation
